ase mt-1\">AI Operations Command Center</h2>\n559 |           <p className=\"text-xs text-white/55 mt-1 leading-relaxed max-w-2xl\">\n560 |             Global administrative terminal. Audit multi-agent runtimes, monitor context frame load indices, and coordinate incident ownership across verified hardware enclaves.\n561 |           </p>\n562 |         </div>\n563 | \n564 |         <div className=\"flex items-center gap-3 self-start md:self-auto font-mono text-[11px] border border-white/5 bg-[#050505]/35 rounded-lg px-3 py-2 text-white/60\">\n565 |           <Activity className={`w-3.5 h-3.5 text-[#00FFC2] shrink-0 ${simulationPulse ? \"opacity-100\" : \"opacity-40\"}`} />\n566 |           <span className=\"text-white/30 uppercase\">Telemetry state:</span>\n567 |           <span className=\"text-[#00FFC2] font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider\">SYNCED</span>\n568 |           <span className=\"text-white/20\">•</span>\n569 |           <span className=\"text-[10px] text-white/40\">EPOCH SEC_2026_A</span>\n570 |         </div>\n571 |       </div>\n572 | \n573 |       {/* --- COMPLIANCE NOTICE BANNER (DO NOT CLAIM LIVE TELEMETRY) --- */}\n574 |       <div className=\"border border-white/5 rounded-xl bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-500/5 to-emerald-500/5 p-4 flex items-start gap-3.5\">\n575 |         <Shield className=\"w-5 h-5 text-[#009DFF] shrink-0 mt-0.5\" />\n576 |         <div className=\"space-y-1\">\n577 |           <div className=\"text-[11px] font-mono uppercase font-bold text-[#009DFF] tracking-wider\">SIMULATION TELEMETRY STREAM ONLY — Standard sandbox compliance auditing mode active.</div>\n578 |           <p className=\"text-[11px] text-white/45 font-mono leading-relaxed max-w-5xl\">\n579 |             This administrative control console operates inside isolated volatile memory spaces. Telemetric streams, CPU partitions (Intel SGX / AMD SEV-SNP), and hardware logs represent verified GFF AI preview models. Actions taken (e.g., owner assignment, diagnostic checks) are modeled locally inside the browser context to demonstrate governance alignment.\n580 |           </p>\n581 |         </div>\n582 |       </div>\n583 | \n584 | \n585 |       {/* --- SECTION 2: HEALTH KPI CARDS GRID --- */}\n586 |       <div className=\"grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-4\">\n587 |         <WorkspaceCard className=\"relative overflow-hidden group\">\n588 |           <div className=\"flex flex-col h-full justify-between gap-3\">\n589 |             <div className=\"flex items-start justify-between\">\n590 |               <div>\n591 |                 <span className=\"text-[9.5px] font-mono tracking-widest text-white/35 uppercase block\">Global Health Index</span>\n592 |                 <span className=\"text-2xl font-bold text-white tracking-tight font-mono mt-1 block\">{overallStats.healthIndex}%</span>\n593 |               </div>\n594 |               <div className=\"p-1.5 rounded-lg border border-emerald-500/20 bg-emerald-500/10 text-emerald-400\">\n595 |                 <CheckCircle2 className=\"w-4 h-4\" />\n596 |               </div>\n597 |             </div>\n598 |             \n599 |             <div className=\"space-y-1.5 mt-2\">\n600 |               <div className=\"flex items-center justify-between text-[10px] font-mono text-white/40 uppercase\">\n601 |                 <span>Core Status Pulse</span>\n602 |                 <span className=\"text-emerald-400 font-bold\">{overallStats.healthIndex === 100 ? \"OPTIMAL\" : \"STABLE BOUNDS\"}</span>\n603 |               </div>\n604 |               <div className=\"flex items-center gap-[2.5px] h-2.5 w-full\">\n605 |                 {Array.from({ length: 24 }).map((_, idx) => {\n606 |                   let bg = \"bg-[#00FFC2]\";\n607 |                   if (idx === 15) bg = \"bg-amber-400\";\n608 |                   if (idx === 21) bg = \"bg-white/10\";\n609 |                   return (\n610 |                     <div \n611 |                       key={idx} \n612 |                       className={`h-full flex-1 rounded-[1.5px] ${bg} opacity-80 hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity`} \n613 |                       title=\"Micro-Node Telemetry Integrity Check\"\n614 |                     />\n615 |                   );\n616 |                 })}\n617 |               </div>\n618 |             </div>\n619 |           </div>\n620 |         </WorkspaceCard>\n621 | \n622 |         <WorkspaceCard className=\"relative overflow-hidden group\">\n623 |           <div className=\"flex flex-col h-full justify-between gap-3\">\n624 |             <div className=\"flex items-start justify-between\">\n625 |               <div>\n626 |                 <span className=\"text-[9.5px] font-mono tracking-widest text-white/35 uppercase block\">Compute Core Allocation</span>\n627 |                 <span className=\"text-2xl font-bold text-white tracking-tight font-mono mt-1 block\">{overallStats.totalThreads} Threads</span>\n628 |               </div>\n629 |               <div className=\"p-1.5 rounded-lg border border-[#009DFF]/20 bg-[#009DFF]/10 text-[#009DFF]\">\n630 |                 <Cpu className=\"w-4 h-4\" />\n631 |               </div>\n632 |             </div>\n633 | \n634 |             <div className=\"space-y-1 mt-2\">\n635 |               <div className=\"flex items-center justify-between text-[10px] font-mono text-white/40\">\n636 |                 <span>SANDBOX CLUSTERS</span>\n637 |                 <span className=\"text-[#009DFF] font-semibold\">{agents.length} Active Runtimes</span>\n638 |               </div>\n639 |               <div className=\"text-[10px] font-mono text-white/30 flex items-center gap-1.5 leading-none\">\n640 |                 <TrendingUp className=\"w-3.5 h-3.5 text-[#00FFC2]\" />\n641 |                 <span className=\"text-[#00FFC2] font-bold\">+12 Cores</span>\n642 |                 <span>since last epoch rotation</span>\n643 |               </div>\n644 |             </div>\n645 |           </div>\n646 |         </WorkspaceCard>\n647 | \n648 |         <WorkspaceCard className=\"relative overflow-hidden group\">\n649 |           <div className=\"flex flex-col h-full justify-between gap-3\">\n650 |             <div className=\"flex items-start justify-between\">\n651 |               <div>\n652 |                 <span className=\"text-[9.5px] font-mono tracking-widest text-white/35 uppercase block\">Mean Heartbeat Latency</span>\n653 |                 <span className=\"text-2xl font-bold text-white tracking-tight font-mono mt-1 block\">{overallStats.meanLatency} ms</span>\n654 |               </div>\n655 |               <div className=\"p-1.5 rounded-lg border border-[#00FFC2]/20 bg-[#00FFC2]/10 text-[#00FFC2]\">\n656 |                 <Clock className=\"w-4 h-4\" />\n657 |               </div>\n658 |             </div>\n659 | \n660 |             <div className=\"space-y-1 mt-2\">\n661 |               <div className=\"flex items-center justify-between text-[10px] font-mono text-white/40\">\n662 |                 <span>ZERO-TRUST TLS WIRE</span>\n663 |                 <span className=\"text-white/60 font-medium\">99.998% Uptime</span>\n664 |               </div>\n665 |               <div className=\"text-[10px] font-mono text-white/30 leading-none\">\n666 |                 Isolated HSM key signatures delay &lt; 2ms\n667 |               </div>\n668 |             </div>\n669 |           </div>\n670 |         </WorkspaceCard>\n671 | \n672 |         <WorkspaceCard className=\"relative overflow-hidden group\">\n673 |           <div className=\"flex flex-col h-full justify-between gap-3\">\n674 |             <div className=\"flex items-start justify-between\">\n675 |               <div>\n676 |                 <span className=\"text-[9.5px] font-mono tracking-widest text-white/35 uppercase block\">Unresolved Governance Incidents</span>\n677 |                 <span className=\"text-2xl font-bold text-[#E4000F] tracking-tight font-mono mt-1 block\">{overallStats.activeAlertsCount} Alerts</span>\n678 |               </div>\n679 |               <div className=\"p-1.5 rounded-lg border border-red-500/20 bg-red-500/10 text-red-400\">\n680 |                 <AlertTriangle className=\"w-4 h-4\" />\n681 |               </div>\n682 |             </div>\n683 | \n684 |             <div className=\"space-y-1 mt-2\">\n685 |               <div className=\"flex items-center justify-between text-[10px] font-mono text-white/40\">\n686 |                 <span>AUDIT ESCALATIONS</span>\n687 |                 <span className=\"text-red-400 font-bold\">1 HIGH PRIORITY</span>\n688 |               </div>\n689 |               <div className=\"text-[10px] font-mono text-white/30 leading-none\">\n690 |                 Awaiting administrative owner sign-off\n691 |               </div>\n692 |             </div>\n693 |           </div>\n694 |         </WorkspaceCard>\n695 |       </div>\n696 | \n697 |       {/* --- SECTION 3: MASTER INTERACTIVE FILTER CONTROL BAR --- */}\n698 |       <div className=\"border border-white/5 rounded-2xl bg-[#050505]/20 backdrop-blur-sm p-4 space-y-4\">\n699 |         <div className=\"flex flex-col md:flex-row md:items-center justify-between gap-3 pb-3 border-b border-white/5\">\n700 |           <div className=\"flex items-center gap-2\">\n701 |             <SlidersHorizontal className=\"w-4 h-4 text-white/45\" />\n702 |             <h3 className=\"text-xs font-mono font-bold uppercase text-white/70 tracking-wider\">Telemetry Routing Filters</h3>\n703 |           </div>\n704 |           {(searchQuery || clientFilter !== \"All\" || projectFilter !== \"All\" || agentTypeFilter !== \"All\" || statusFilter !== \"All\" || severityFilter !== \"All\" || ownerFilter !== \"All\") && (\n705 |             <button\n706 |               onClick={handleResetFilters}\n707 |               className=\"text-[10px] font-mono text-[#009DFF] hover:text-white flex items-center gap-1 transition-colors uppercase font-bold cursor-pointer\"\n708 |             >\n709 |               <X className=\"w-3 h-3\" />\n710 |               <span>Reset Filters</span>\n711 |             </button>\n712 |           )}\n713 |         </div>\n714 | \n715 |         <div className=\"grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 lg:grid-cols-7 gap-3\">\n716 |           <div className=\"col-span-2 md:col-span-2 flex flex-col gap-1.5\">\n717 |             <label className=\"text-[9px] font-mono text-white/30 uppercase font-bold tracking-wider font-semibold\">Search Node Parameters</label>\n718 |             <div className=\"relative\">\n719 |               <Search className=\"absolute left-2.5 top-2.5 h-3.5 w-3.5 text-white/35 pointer-events-none\" />\n720 |               <input\n721 |                 type=\"text\"\n722 |                 placeholder=\"Search agent name, ID, logs...\"\n723 |                 value={searchQuery}\n724 |                 onChange={(e) => setSearchQuery(e.target.value)}\n725 |                 className=\"w-full bg-white/[0.01] hover:bg-white/[0.03] focus:bg-white/[0.05] border border-white/5 focus:border-[#009DFF]/30 rounded-lg pl-8 pr-3 py-1.5 text-[11px] font-mono text-white outline-none placeholder:text-white/25 transition-all\"\n726 |               />\n727 |             </div>\n728 |           </div>\n729 | \n730 |           <div className=\"flex flex-col gap-1.5\">\n731 |             <label className=\"text-[9px] font-mono text-white/30 uppercase font-bold tracking-wider font-semibold\">Client Account</label>\n732 |             <select\n733 |               value={clientFilter}\n734 |               onChange={(e) => setClientFilter(e.target.value)}\n735 |               className=\"w-full bg-[#050505] hover:bg-white/[0.04] border border-white/5 hover:border-white/10 rounded-lg px-2.5 py-1.5 text-[11px] font-mono text-white/70 hover:text-white transition-all outline-none cursor-pointer\"\n736 |             >\n737 |               <option value=\"All\">ALL CLIENTS</option>\n738 |               {UNIQUE_CLIENTS.map(c => (\n739 |                 <option key={c} value={c}>\n740 |                   {c.replace(\" [Preview Client]\", \"\")}\n741 |                 </option>\n742 |               ))}\n743 |             </select>\n744 |           </div>\n745 | \n746 |           <div className=\"flex flex-col gap-1.5\">\n747 |             <label className=\"text-[9px] font-mono text-white/30 uppercase font-bold tracking-wider font-semibold\">Project Layer</label>\n748 |             <select\n749 |               value={projectFilter}\n750 |               onChange={(e) => setProjectFilter(e.target.value)}\n751 |               className=\"w-full bg-[#050505] hover:bg-white/[0.04] border border-white/5 hover:border-white/10 rounded-lg px-2.5 py-1.5 text-[11px] font-mono text-white/70 hover:text-white transition-all outline-none cursor-pointer\"\n752 |             >\n753 |               <option value=\"All\">ALL PROJECTS</option>\n754 |               {UNIQUE_PROJECTS.map(p => (\n755 |                 <option key={p} value={p}>\n756 |                   {p}\n757 |                 </option>\n758 |               ))}\n759 |             </select>\n760 |           </div>\n761 | \n762 |           <div className=\"flex flex-col gap-1.5\">\n763 |             <label className=\"text-[9px] font-mono text-white/30 uppercase font-bold tracking-wider font-semibold\">Classification</label>\n764 |             <select\n765 |               value={agentTypeFilter}\n766 |               onChange={(e) => setAgentTypeFilter(e.target.value)}\n767 |               className=\"w-full bg-[#050505] hover:bg-white/[0.04] border border-white/5 hover:border-white/10 rounded-lg px-2.5 py-1.5 text-[11px] font-mono text-white/70 hover:text-white transition-all outline-none cursor-pointer\"\n768 |             >\n769 |               <option value=\"All\">ALL CLASSIFICATIONS</option>\n770 |               {UNIQUE_TYPES.map(t => (\n771 |                 <option key={t} value={t}>\n772 |                   {t}\n773 |                 </option>\n774 |               ))}\n775 |             </select>\n776 |           </div>\n777 | \n778 |           <div className=\"flex flex-col gap-1.5\">\n779 |             <label className=\"text-[9px] font-mono text-white/30 uppercase font-bold tracking-wider font-semibold\">Telemetry Pulse</label>\n780 |             <select\n781 |               value={statusFilter}\n782 |               onChange={(e) => setStatusFilter(e.target.value)}\n783 |               className=\"w-full bg-[#050505] hover:bg-white/[0.04] border border-white/5 hover:border-white/10 rounded-lg px-2.5 py-1.5 text-[11px] font-mono text-white/70 hover:text-white transition-all outline-none cursor-pointer\"\n784 |             >\n785 |               <option value=\"All\">ALL PULSES</option>\n786 |               {UNIQUE_STATUSES.map(s => (\n787 |                 <option key={s} value={s} className=\"uppercase font-mono\">\n788 |                   {s.toUpperCase()}\n789 |                 </option>\n790 |               ))}\n791 |             </select>\n792 |           </div>\n793 | \n794 |           <div className=\"flex flex-col gap-1.5\">\n795 |             <label className=\"text-[9px] font-mono text-white/30 uppercase font-bold tracking-wider font-semibold\">Assigned Operator</label>\n796 |             <select\n797 |               value={ownerFilter}\n798 |               onChange={(e) => setOwnerFilter(e.target.value)}\n799 |               className=\"w-full bg-[#050505] hover:bg-white/[0.04] border border-white/5 hover:border-white/10 rounded-lg px-2.5 py-1.5 text-[11px] font-mono text-white/70 hover:text-white transition-all outline-none cursor-pointer\"\n800 |             >\n801 |               <option value=\"All\">ALL OPERATORS</option>\n802 |               {OWNERS.map(o => (\n803 |                 <option key={o} value={o}>\n804 |                   {o}\n805 |                 </option>\n806 |               ))}\n807 |             </select>\n808 |           </div>\n809 |         </div>\n810 |       </div>\n811 | \n812 | \n813 |       {/* --- SECTION 4: DOUBLE CORRELATION BOARD (AGENTS TABLE & ALERTS SIDEBAR) --- */}\n814 |       <div className=\"grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-6 items-start\">\n815 |         {/* LEFT COLUMN (COLSPAN 3): ACTIVE AGENTS OPERATION TERMINAL */}\n816 |         <div className=\"lg:col-span-3 border border-white/5 rounded-2xl bg-[#050505]/40 backdrop-blur-sm overflow-hidden flex flex-col\">\n817 |           <div className=\"bg-white/[0.02] border-b border-white/5 px-4 py-3 flex items-center justify-between\">\n818 |             <div className=\"flex items-center gap-2 text-[10px] font-mono text-white/40 uppercase font-bold tracking-wider\">\n819 |               <Bot className=\"w-4 h-4 text-[#009DFF]\" />\n820 |               <span>Multi-Agent Sovereign Runtimes ({filteredAgents.length})</span>\n821 |             </div>\n822 |             <div className=\"text-[10.5px] font-mono text-white/30 flex items-center gap-1.5\">\n823 |               <RefreshCw className={`w-3 h-3 text-[#009DFF] ${simulationPulse ? \"animate-spin\" : \"\"}`} />\n824 |               <span>Real-time sweep active</span>\n825 |             </div>\n826 |           </div>\n827 | \n828 |           <div className=\"overflow-x-auto\">\n829 |             <table className=\"w-full min-w-[900px] text-left font-mono text-[11px] text-white/70\">\n830 |               <thead>\n831 |                 <tr className=\"border-b border-white/5 text-white/35 text-[9.5px] uppercase font-bold bg-white/[0.01]\">\n832 |                   <th className=\"p-4\">Agent ID / Name</th>\n833 |                   <th className=\"p-4\">Enterprise Bounds</th>\n834 |                   <th className=\"p-4\">Classification</th>\n835 |                   <th className=\"p-4\">Compute allocation</th>\n836 |                   <th className=\"p-4\">Pulse State</th>\n837 |                   <th className=\"p-4\">Severity</th>\n838 |                   <th className=\"p-4\">Local Assignee</th>\n839 |                   <th className=\"p-4 t